== Months of Kōshin == In years where the last digit is 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft}} is {{ill|壬|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft}} or {{ill|丁|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月|12=draft}} is a Kōshin month. However, this may also be calculated using the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft}} months or the {{ill|Solar Terms|ja|節月|12=draft}}, meaning the period from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Lixia|ja|立夏|12=draft}}.
== Days of Kōshin == === Selection Days === A Kōshin day is the 12th day of {{ill|Tennichitenjō|ja|天一天上|12=draft}}.
