{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Wood Dragon|kanji=甲辰|romaji=kinoe tatsu|onyomi=kōshin|p=jiǎchén|w=chia-ch'en|mi=ʈ͡ʂja̠²¹ ʈʂʰən|y=gaap6 san4|j=gaap6 san4|ci=kaːp̚ sɐn|mc=kæp ɖin|oc-bs=kaːp ɖiŋ}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yang Wood Dragon''', also known as {{ill|Kōshin|ja|甲辰|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (''Kinoe-tatsu, Kōboku-no-tatsu, Kōshin, Chinsō-no-tatsu''), is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
It is the 41st combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and preceding {{ill|乙巳|ja|乙巳|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. In {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|甲|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents the {{ill|Yang|ja|陽|qq=draft|qq=draft}} aspect of {{ill|Wood|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, while {{ill|辰|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents the Yang aspect of {{ill|Earth|ja|土|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. This combination is classified as an instance of {{ill|Mutual Controlling (Wood Controls Earth)|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Years of Kōshin == A year in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 44 corresponds to the year of Kōshin. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Kōshin''' |- ![[1st Millennium]]!![[2nd Millennium]]!![[3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[44]] * [[104]] * [[164]] * [[224]] * [[284]] * [[344]] * [[404]] * [[464]] * [[524]] * [[584]] * [[644]] * [[704]] * [[764]] * [[824]] * [[884]] * [[944]] | * [[1004]] * [[1064]] * [[1124]] * [[1184]] * [[1244]] * [[1304]] * [[1364]] * [[1424]] * [[1484]] * [[1544]] * [[1604]] * [[1664]] * [[1724]] * [[1784]] * [[1844]] * [[1904]] * [[1964]] | * [[2024]] * [[2084]] * [[2144]] * [[2204]] * [[2264]] * [[2324]] * [[2384]] * [[2444]] * [[2504]] * [[2564]] * [[2624]] * [[2684]] * [[2744]] * [[2804]] * [[2864]] * [[2924]] * [[2984]] |}
== Months of Kōshin == In years where the last digit is 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is {{ill|壬|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or {{ill|丁|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is a Kōshin month. However, this may also be calculated using the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} months or the {{ill|Solar Terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, meaning the period from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Lixia|ja|立夏|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
== Days of Kōshin == === Selection Days === A Kōshin day is the 12th day of {{ill|Tennichitenjō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. ==See Also== *{{prefix}} *{{intitle}} {{citation needed|きのえたつ}}
