It is the 41st combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|1=Yin Water Rabbit|2=ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|ja|1=Yin Water Rabbit|2=ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/癸卯|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rabbit|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|1=Yin Wood Snake|2=ja|乙巳|ja|1=Yin Wood Snake|2=ja|乙巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/乙巳|qq=}}. In {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, {{ill|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|lt=Kinoe (甲)|2=ja|3=甲|4=zh|5=甲|qq=}} represents the {{ill|Yang|ja|陽|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang|qq=}} aspect of {{ill|Wood|ja|Wood (木)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood|qq=}}, while {{ill|辰|1=Dragon (Zodiac)|lt=Dragon (辰)|2=ja|3=辰|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/辰|qq=}} represents the Yang aspect of {{ill|Earth|ja|Earth (土)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|2=ru|3=Земля (у-син)|4=mn|5=Шороо (махбод)|6=uk|7=Земля (У-сін)|8=als|9=Ärde in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|10=bcl|11=Daga (wuxing)|12=vi|13=Thổ (Ngũ hành)|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}. This combination is classified as an instance of {{ill|Mutual Controlling (Wood Controls Earth)|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|lt=相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Controlling (Wood Controls Earth)|qq=}}.
== Years of Kōshin == A year in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 44 corresponds to the year of Kōshin. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Kōshin''' |- ![[1st Millennium]]!![[2nd Millennium]]!![[3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[44]] * [[104]] * [[164]] * [[224]] * [[284]] * [[344]] * [[404]] * [[464]] * [[524]] * [[584]] * [[644]] * [[704]] * [[764]] * [[824]] * [[884]] * [[944]] | * [[1004]] * [[1064]] * [[1124]] * [[1184]] * [[1244]] * [[1304]] * [[1364]] * [[1424]] * [[1484]] * [[1544]] * [[1604]] * [[1664]] * [[1724]] * [[1784]] * [[1844]] * [[1904]] * [[1964]] | * [[2024]] * [[2084]] * [[2144]] * [[2204]] * [[2264]] * [[2324]] * [[2384]] * [[2444]] * [[2504]] * [[2564]] * [[2624]] * [[2684]] * [[2744]] * [[2804]] * [[2864]] * [[2924]] * [[2984]] |}
== Months of Kōshin == In years where the last digit is 2 or 7 (where the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} is {{ill|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/壬|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/丁|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|March|ja|3月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March|qq=}} is a Kōshin month. However, this may also be calculated using the {{ill|Lunar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} months or the {{ill|Solar Terms|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar Terms|qq=}}, meaning the period from {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Lixia|ja|立夏|1=Lixia|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lixia|qq=}}.
== Days of Kōshin == === Selection Days === A Kōshin day is the 12th day of {{ill|Tennichitenjō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tennichitenjō|qq=}}. ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
