'''Yang Wood Dragon''', also known as {{ill|Kōshin|ja|1=Yang Wood Dragon|2=ja|甲辰|1=Yang Wood Dragon|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōshin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōshin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Wood Dragon|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (''Kinoe-tatsu, Kōboku-no-tatsu, Kōshin, Chinsō-no-tatsu''), is one of the [[:en:Sexagenary cycle|Sexagenary cycle]].
It is the 41st combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|1=Yin Water Rabbit|2=ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|ja|1=Yin Water Rabbit|2=ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/癸卯|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rabbit|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1=Yin Water Rabbit|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rabbit|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|1=Yin Wood Snake|2=ja|乙巳|ja|1=Yin Wood Snake|2=ja|乙巳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/乙巳|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1=Yin Wood Snake|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Wood Snake|qq=}}. In {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Kinoe (甲)]] represents the {{ill|Yang|ja|陽|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=陰陽|comment=changed title based on wikidata|1=yin and yang|WD=Q62744}} aspect of {{ill|Wood|ja|Wood (木)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|